ants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"When William Freebody was born in 1400, in West Bromwich, Staffordshire, England, his father, William Freebody, was 25 and his mother, Alice Freeman, was 20. He had at least 1 son with Rachel Freeman. He died in 1437, in his hometown, at the age of 37."},"et":{"1400–1437":"1400–1437","1402–Female":"1402–Surnud","1426–1502":"1426–1502","1375–Male":"1375–Surnud","1380–Female":"1380–Surnud","1426":"1426","1437":"1437","1502":"1502","1402":"1402","1400":"1400","1375":"1375","1380":"1380","West Bromwich, Staffordshire, England":"West Bromwich, Staffordshire, England"},"fi":{"1400–1437":"1400–1437","1402–Female":"1402–Kuollut","1426–1502":"1426–1502","1375–Male":"1375–Kuollut","1380–Female":"1380–Kuollut","1426":"1426","1437":"1437","1502":"1502","1402":"1402","1400":"1400","1375":"1375","1380":"1380","West Bromwich, Staffordshire, England":"West Bromwich, Staffordshire, England"},"fr":{"1400–1437":"1400–1437","1402–Female":"1402–Décédée","1426–1502":"1426–1502","1375–Male":"1375–Décédé","1380–Female":"1380–Décédée","1426":"1426","1437":"1437","1502":"1502","1402":"1402","1400":"1400","1375":"1375","1380":"1380","West Bromwich, Staffordshire, England":"West Bromwich, Staffordshire, Angleterre","lifeSummary":"Lorsque William Freebody est né en 1400, à West Bromwich, Staffordshire, Angleterre, son père, William Freebody, avait 25 ans et sa mère, Alice Freeman, avait 20 ans. Il a eu au moins 1 fils avec Rachel Freeman. Il est décédé en 1437, dans sa ville natale, à l’âge de 37 ans."},"de":{"1400–1437":"1400–1437","1402–Female":"1402–Verstorben","1426–1502":"1426–1502","1375–Male":"1375–Verstorben","1380–Female":"1380–Verstorben","1426":"1426","1437":"1437","1502":"1502","1402":"1402","1400":"1400","1375":"1375","1380":"1380","West Bromwich, Staffordshire, England":"West Bromwich, Staffordshire, England","lifeSummary":"Als William Freebody 1400 in West Bromwich, Staffordshire, England geboren wurde, war sein Vater William Freebody 25 und seine Mutter